about.inbox.intro1: You are now viewing an early version of the new Altinn inbox. Eventually it will replace the current inbox, and we are working on transferring old messages.
about.inbox.intro2: The new inbox is part of
about.inbox.section.availability.link: the inbox you are familiar with.
about.inbox.section.availability.p1: Since Altinn is used by many public sector organizations and everything must work together, changes are rolled out gradually. You may therefore experience that old messages are missing or appear differently in the new inbox.
about.inbox.section.availability.p2: Not all content has been transferred yet, and until all service owners have adopted the new inbox, you must also use
about.inbox.section.availability.title: Will I find everything in the new inbox?
about.inbox.section.dialogs.li1: Is the case completed or does it require action? Dialogues can be marked with a status to help you understand what is most important.
about.inbox.section.dialogs.li2: What has happened? What’s new, when was the dialogue updated? Who has viewed the dialogue? More information makes it easier to distinguish between dialogues.
about.inbox.section.dialogs.p1: The idea with Altinn is to gather all digital communication with the public sector, but it is not always easy to keep track of all the messages you receive. In the new inbox, agencies can group messages that belong to the same case in a single dialogue. You also get more information to help you stay organized.
about.inbox.section.dialogs.title: Better dialogues
about.inbox.section.feedback.email: please feel free to email us.
about.inbox.section.feedback.p1: If you have questions or feedback,
about.inbox.section.feedback.title: Give us feedback
search.results.description: The most recently updated results are shown first.
about.inbox.section.find.li1: Better search: For now, you can only search for single words, but we are working to improve the search experience.
about.inbox.section.find.li2: Better filtering options: Looking for a dialogue from a specific agency or with a certain status? Use filters to narrow the results.
about.inbox.section.find.li3: Cross-inbox search: If you have access to multiple inboxes, you can search across them simultaneously.
about.inbox.section.find.p1: We know many users have large, complex inboxes. That’s why we are working on making it easier to locate old dialogues.
about.inbox.section.find.title: Easier to navigate
about.inbox.title: New inbox – better dialogues, easier to navigate
